<p>Five performance measures were applied including balanced accuracy (BA, Equation (1)) [
 <xref rid="B39-biomolecules-10-01605" ref-type="bibr">39</xref>], Matthew’s correlation coefficient (MCC, Equation (2)) [
 <xref rid="B40-biomolecules-10-01605" ref-type="bibr">40</xref>], F1 score (Equation (3)) [
 <xref rid="B41-biomolecules-10-01605" ref-type="bibr">41</xref>], precision (Equation (4)), and recall (Equation (5)). 
